title: Starfish Dancer
description: Female dancing figure standing on demi-toe, hands together above head, costumed in reptile texture, brown, with gold decoration covering figure completely, except face and hands which are ivory and are finely chiseled.  Base of onyx pieces of various colors, mostly brown/beige, in various geometric shapes.
